#. Tag: para
#: details-schedules.docbook:313
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This information can be changed, and the changes can be applied to just "
#| "this one instance of the schedule or to all subsequent transactions. "
#| "After checking that all the data is correct clicking on <guibutton>OK</"
#| "guibutton> will add the transaction to the ledger and update the next due "
